On January 17, it was reported that Zhang Tianfeng, former deputy director of the State Tobacco Administration, was under investigation for suspected serious violations of discipline and law;
On December 6 last year, it was reported that Xu Yu, former deputy director of the State Tobacco Administration, was arrested;
On November 25, it was reported that Ling Chengxing, former director of the State Tobacco Administration, was investigated for corruption of a particularly large amount of money;
On May 29, it was reported that He Zehua, former deputy director of the State Tobacco Administration, was sentenced to death with a reprieve.
